title: NFL 2019 Midseason Awards, MVP Race, Predictions (Football 10/30)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Brady Quinn and Ryan Wilson to give their midseason picks for NFL awards as well as declaring who they think will win at the end of the season. The guys cover the race for Offensive Rookie of the Year, Defensive Rookie of the Year, Coach of the Year, Defensive Player of the Year, Offensive Rookie of the Year and MVP. Will, Brady and Ryan also take a look at the 2020 NFL Draft and why a non-QB could go number one overall, before answering your questions from 5-star reviews on Apple Podcasts.
